room_title: Escape room "Prison Break" by Rexburg Re-Escapes in Rexburg
room_description: You have been in prison for a while, but you are set to be released tomorrow. Unfortunately, you didn't give Big Joe your dessert at meal-time, so he has bribed some of the prison guards to handcuff and lock you in an old cell so Big Joe can "have a chat" with you. You have an hour before he arrives.
